title: CIP0001-Club721 advertisement income
body:
As we approaching 20k members in discord, we have constantly projects reaching out to us, but we have been rejecting all of them since we did not want to take money to advertise their projects regardless of how good it is, just like we dropped our Club721 NFT for free too as it is believed in our vision.

Now community gets to decide if we should pick up advertisement revenue or not. 

All income goes to Club721 reserve fund, you can vote of using it the way you like, or simply split those ETH to all Club721 NFT holders.

It will be a way to reward Club721 NFT holders
choices: NO - keep it clean and AD free
author: 0x8c0d2B62F133Db265EC8554282eE60EcA0Fd5a9E
